campus this Saturday; you may place your order in advance and pick up at school.','MCS Newsletter - 3/12/2011',0,'','publish','closed','open','','mcs-newsletter-3122011','','','2011-03-09 19:32:45','2011-03-09 23:32:45','',0,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=134',0,'post','',0),(135,1,'2011-03-09 19:32:28','2011-03-09 23:32:28','','MCS Newsletter - 3/12/2011',0,'','inherit','open','open','','134-revision','','','2011-03-09 19:32:28','2011-03-09 23:32:28','',134,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=135',0,'revision','',0),(136,1,'2011-03-16 20:44:00','2011-03-17 00:44:00','<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Appreciation</span></strong>\r\n\r\nThanks to賴哲琛, 劉怡均(Allen Lai &amp; Julia Liu) donating their referral fee to school. Also\r\n\r\nThanks to 陳俐君 (Tracy Wu) donating her cupcakes sales last week to school.\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Presentation – Preparing for College </span></strong>\r\n\r\nWe are glad to have Kelley Wu (吳可琳) Admission Advisor at Eastern Michigan University\r\n\r\n(2004 密西根中文學校畢業)  come to our school this week (3/19) to have a presentation for all  parents and G-10 students. The presentation will be based on Admission  adviser view point on how to prepare for college. She will give a  presentation and after that open the floor for questions. Please invite  anyone who may be interested in this topic. Presentation starts at 1:45  pm. at Parents Lounge.\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Speech Contest </span></strong>\r\n\r\nPlease mark your calendar, MCS speech contest is scheduled on Saturday 4/9/2011.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Fund Raising </span></strong>\r\n\r\nAs usual, we will have QQ bakery as our school fund raising this Saturday. Don\'t miss it and be there in time.','MCS Newsletter - 3/19/2011',0,'','publish','closed','open','','mcs-newsletter-3192011','','','2011-03-16 20:44:00','2011-03-17 00:44:00','',0,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=136',0,'post','',0),(137,1,'2011-03-16 20:43:26','2011-03-17 00:43:26','','MCS Newsletter - 3/19/2011',0,'','inherit','open','open','','136-revision','','','2011-03-16 20:43:26','2011-03-17 00:43:26','',136,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=137',0,'revision','',0),(138,1,'2011-03-23 23:31:38','2011-03-24 03:31:38','<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Appreciation</span></strong>\r\n\r\nThanks to Kelley Wu (吳可琳)  \"Planning for College\" presentation last week. We had G-10 students and  parents attend this presentation. Many questions were discussed during  this one hour presentation. We also want to thanks Shee-Tak Loh (陸樹德) who spent time to make this event happened.\r\n\r\nYou can find completed presentation material in our school Website.\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">QQ Bakery on Break </span></strong>\r\n\r\nMany  of you were disappointed when founded out there was no QQ bakery fund  raising last week. This is because the owner of QQ bakery is on vacation  and store is closed for three weeks. We didn\'t know this till last  Friday.\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Speech Contest </span></strong>\r\n\r\nPlease  mark your calendar, MCS speech contest is scheduled on Saturday  4/9/2011. The top three place students will have the chance to attend  Interschool Speech Contest on 5/7/2011 which is hosted by our school.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">健康講座</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Seminar </span></strong>\r\n\r\n密西根中華婦女會將於四月十日舉辦<strong>健康講座</strong>，時間是下午5:00-7:30，地點為West Bloomfield 圖書館會議廳。健康講座是免費入場並提供披薩晚餐。\r\n\r\n密西根州社區健康部疾病防治中心 (DHWDC) 專門負責少數族群健康部門，訂定四月份為「少數族群月」，因之提供款項資助少數族群開辦活動，目的在促進少數族群對健保改革和(或) 推動學童在校營養午餐有更詳盡的認知。<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">密西根州東南亞裔中心</span> (Asia Center-SE MI) 於今年一月申請專款辦理對健保改革認知活動，並於二月份獲選。該款項將可提供兩項主要活動：一為在四月二日為各個協辦單位所舉辦的訓練會，另一則是舉辦四場說明會，盼能將健保改革的訊息傳遞到各不同族群的角落。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">密西根中華婦女會</span>是<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">密西根州東南亞裔中心</span>辦理此活動的協辦單位之一。四月十日當天的健康講座上，<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">密西根州東南亞裔中心</span>主任既負責人<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">楊</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">芷雯</span>(Janilla Lee )博士將擔任主講人。<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">楊</span>博士 曾在福特汽車公司擔任高階主管。退休後到<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">密西根大會</span>研習亞裔美人 (Asian American) 健康。她從1996 年起開始關心健康問題並對此問題始終不遺餘力的努力。此次活動經費既<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">楊</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">芷雯</span>博士申請來的。四月十日她將針對<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">歐巴馬</span>總統所提出的「健保改革案」對少數族群的影響，做深入的解釋。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">密西根中華婦女會</span>在四月十日活動中也將邀請<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">王鴻烈</span>牙醫博士及<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">林妙娟</span>牙醫博士賢伉儷為與會人士講解 「如何做好牙齒的健康保健和復健」。<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">王鴻烈</span>博士目前是密西根大學牙周病研究所所長，也是牙周病和植牙權威且經常在世界各地發表演講。<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">林妙娟</span>牙醫博士，畢業於<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">密西根大學</span>，已行醫 十七年，目前在勒佛尼亞 (Livonia) 開設牙醫診所。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">密西根中華婦女會</span>於四月十日舉辦的健康講座內容與我們生活有直接的關係，所邀請到的主講人也都是在該專業中的頂尖代表人物，屆時必能提供最佳資訊，希望大家能踴躍出席。場地有限, 有意參加者，請與活動負責人報名:  傅曼玲 (248-705-6334) 侯珞怡 (248-788-7934) 韓燕如 (248-788-4669) 王禎楣 (248-641-7761)。','MCS Newsletter - 3/26/2011',0,'','publish','closed','open','','mcs-newsletter-3262011','','','2011-03-23 23:31:38','2011-03-24 03:31:38','',0,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=138',0,'post','',0),(139,1,'2011-03-23 23:30:42','2011-03-24 03:30:42','','MCS Newslett