30 22:35:06','2011-03-31 02:35:06','',140,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=141',0,'revision','',0),(142,1,'2011-04-06 23:10:32','2011-04-07 03:10:32','MCS Newsletter                              April 9, 2011\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>MCS will have 2011 speech contest this Saturday (4/9/2011) and there will be no regular class.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>All students and teachers should check in at Take Five Lounge.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Student/Parents  should receive detail information from teacher. If you don’t receive  any schedule, please contact your teacher direct.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">\r\n</span></strong>','MCS Newsletter - 4/9/2011',0,'','publish','closed','open','','mcs-newsletter-492011','','','2011-04-06 23:10:32','2011-04-07 03:10:32','',0,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=142',0,'post','',0),(143,1,'2011-04-06 23:10:15','2011-04-07 03:10:15','','MCS Newsletter - 4/9/2011',0,'','inherit','open','open','','142-revision','','','2011-04-06 23:10:15','2011-04-07 03:10:15','',142,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=143',0,'revision','',0),(144,1,'2011-04-13 23:20:00','2011-04-14 03:20:00','<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Speech Contest </span></strong>\r\n\r\nThanks  to everyone\'s support, we had speech contest last week. We really  appreciated students\' preparation, teachers\' hard work and volunteers  from parents/staff. Below  is the final award list and all top three students from each group will  have the opportunity to represent our school to participate interschool  speech contest on 5/7/2011.  If  any student missed the award ceremony and didn\'t get the trophy last  week, please report to teacher and we will have trophy ready.\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"452\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr height=\"20\">\r\n<td width=\"92\" height=\"20\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"20\" valign=\"bottom\">第一名</td>\r\n<td w