lign=\"bottom\">王淨德</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\">張智詠</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr height=\"19\">\r\n<td width=\"92\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\">看圖說故事</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\">鄺紹耘</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\">張智詠</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr height=\"19\">\r\n<td width=\"92\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\">陳楷文</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\">吳明翰</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"19\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr height=\"20\">\r\n<td width=\"92\" height=\"20\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"20\" valign=\"bottom\">王淨德</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"20\" valign=\"bottom\">萬雨威</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"20\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"20\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\" height=\"20\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\nThanks to Sylvia Richards ( 劉蔚芝) taking the pictures during award ceremony. Follow the link below you will see the event pictures and you may download the ones you like.\r\n\r\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://picasaweb.google.com/snap2shot/20110409ChineseScoolSpeech?authkey=Gv1sRgCP_czL-AvIGahwE&amp;feat=directlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://picasaweb.google.com/snap2shot/20110409ChineseScoolSpeech?authkey=Gv1sRgCP_czL-AvIGahwE&amp;feat=directlink</a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong> </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong> </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Fund Raising </span></strong>\r\n\r\nLast  month, due to bakery owner on vacation, we were unable to have this  event. But now, it\'s back. We will have QQ bakery as our school fund  raising this Saturday and all bakery will be picked up on Saturday  morning. So it\'s very fresh! Don\'t miss it and be there in time.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">No School 4/23/2011</span>\r\n\r\nThere will be no school on Saturday 4/23/2011.','MCS Newsletter - 4/16/2011',0,'','publish','closed','open','','mcs-newsletter-4162011','','','2011-04-13 23:20:00','2011-04-14 03:20:00','',0,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=144',0,'post','',0),(145,1,'2011-04-27 22:19:25','2011-04-28 02:19:25','MCS Newsletter                              April 30, 2011\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Upcoming Events</span></strong>\r\n\r\n5/7/2011   Interschool Speech Contest. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>No School</strong></span>\r\n\r\n5/14/2011 All Parents Meeting &amp;  2011-2012 Vice Principal nomination/election\r\n\r\n5/21/2011 Fund Raising (Bake Sale, Tooth Paste Sale and more)\r\n\r\n5/28/2011 No School\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Interschool Speech Contest </span></strong>\r\n\r\nThis  annual event will take place on 5/7/2011 and this year will have  students from Ann Arbor Chinese School, Southern Michigan Chinese School  and MDCAC Chinese School. Total (75) students compete in eight  different groups. We have many volunteers from our parents, staff and  teachers to help organize this event. Everyone is welcome to this event.  Event location will be at Madonna University and begins at 1:30 pm.\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Teachers Survey</span></strong>\r\n\r\nLast  year, we had teacher survey and reviewed the result with each  individual teacher letting they know what\'s the feedback from their  class. We are going to have second teacher survey and its due 4/30. We  would like to hear from you to see any improvement has been made since  last survey. After receiving survey, we will have one staff summarize  the survey and re-type in computer file. We will combine both surveys  summary then provide a copy to each teacher and existing Vice Principal  for future reference. <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><em>Your honest  comment is needed and we guarantee this is an anonymous survey. If you  don\'t have survey form, please contact your class parent rep.</em></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Application for Graduation</span></strong>\r\n\r\n10<sup>th</sup> graders and their parents, if you/your child are qualified for  graduation this year, talk to your teacher to apply for graduation.','MCS Newsletter - 4/30/2011',0,'','publish','closed','open','','mcs-newsletter-4302011','','','2011-04-27 22:19:25','2011-04-28 02:19:25','',0,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=145',0,'post','',0),(146,1,'2011-04-27 22:19:04','2011-04-28 02:19:04','','MCS Newsletter - 4/30/2011',0,'','inherit','open','open','','145-revision','','','2011-04-27 22:19:04','2011-04-28 02:19:04','',145,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=146',0,'revision','',0),(147,1,'2011-05-11 22:41:13','2011-05-12 02:41:13','MCS Newsletter                              May 14, 2011\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Appreciation</span></strong>\r\n\r\nThank to 葉易凡和張翊威cash donation to Michigan Chinese School\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Upcoming Events</span></strong>\r\n\r\n5/14/2011 All Parents Meeting &amp;  2011-2012 VP nomination/election\r\n\r\n5/21/2011 Fund Raising (Bake Sale, Tooth Paste Sale, Book sales and more)\r\n\r\n5/28/2011 Memory Weekend. No School\r\n\r\n6/4/2011   DIY Home Monitoring System Presentation / QQ Bakery\r\n\r\n6/11/2011 Graduation Ceremony\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Interschool Speech Contest </span></strong>\r\n\r\nThis  annual event took place on 5/7/2011 and we had students from Michigan  Chinese School , Ann Arbor Chinese School , Southern Michigan Chinese  School and MDCAC Chinese School . Total (75) students competed in eight  different groups. We had many volunteers from our parents, staff,  teachers and 10<sup>th</sup> grade students to help organize this event.  The weather was perfect and several staff started their preparation as  early as 11:30 am. After almost three hours event, everyone stopped by  Take Five Lounge to enjoy the healthy and tasty snack. By the way, all  participating students got a trophy and a gift home.\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"488\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">第一名</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">第二名</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\">第三名</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">演講比賽</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">第一組</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">顏欣俞 (安娜堡)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">易樂人 (南密)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\">林楷晞 (密西根)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">第二組</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">徐偉恩 (安娜堡)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">林韶安 (安娜堡)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\">楊咏霖 (密西根)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">第三組</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">魏郁安 (密西根)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">丘宸宇 (南密)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\">石蜜雅 (南密)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">第四組</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">張岳琳 (南密)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">王淨慧 (密西根)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"top\">孫立誠 (宣道會)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">第五組</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">丘丞崴 (南密)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">邱皓 (密西根)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\">陳柏年 (南密)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">第六組</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"top\">詹皓全 (宣道會)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">看圖說故事</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">第七組</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">孫偉恩 (南密)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">陳楷文 (密西根)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">周韋宏 (南密)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">徐以衡 (密西根)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">王德軒 (密西根)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\">第八組</td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">易韶人 (南密)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">鄺紹耘 (密西根)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">李雙安 (南密)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">陳毅恩 (密西根)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"92\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"136\" valign=\"bottom\">馬翊晴 (南密)</td>\r\n<td width=\"133\" valign=\"bottom\">王淨德 (密西根)</td>\r\n<td width=\"127\" valign=\"bottom\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Year End All Parents Meeting</span></strong>\r\n\r\nIt\'s  that time again, current staff and I will prepare to present what we  have accomplished 2010-2011 school year. Also we are going to have next  Vice Principal nomination. If we have enough attendance, we could have  the election at the same time. Please plan to attend this annual  meeting. Meeting begins at1:30 pm at Parents Lounge.\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Fund Raising</span></strong>\r\n\r\nMany  parents request school to have a Fun/Fund Raising before end of school  not only to raising money for school, but also to bring all kinds of  delicious food for school families. We will have this first time ever  event on May 21 which include the following:\r\n\r\nØ      <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Book Sales</span>: there are some brand new text books from school inventory. Some parents will bring used reading material for a great deal.\r\n\r\nØ      <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Tooth Paste Sales</span>: Thanks to Dentist Holly Lin who donated high quality tooth paste to school and all sales will go to school funding.\r\n\r\nØ      <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Bake Sales</span>:  Parents who is willing to bring in food of any kind, you may help  school funding by donate all your sales to school. So far we have the  following from parents:\r\n\r\n蜂蜜蛋糕 ,碗粿, 花生豆花, 蔥油大餅.   If you are interested and plan to participate in this bake sales, please contact Jessica Lee (陳惠昭) and let her know what you are bring in so we won\'t have duplicated. <strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">8<sup>th</sup> Grade Composition Exhibition </span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">作文展覽</span></strong><strong></strong>\r\n\r\n8<sup>th</sup> grade class will have students writing exhibition next two weeks in  front of parents lounge. All parents and students are welcome to stop  by.\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Proposed CSL Class Next Year</span></strong>\r\n\r\nIt was proposed by a couple of current 1<sup>st</sup> grade parents to have a new CSL class next year. The target students  for this new CSL class will be 5-10 years old children who don\'t have  Chinese speaking environment at home. The teaching material will be  based on 拼音Pin-Ying (not traditional 注音符號).  We would like to have our parents wide spread this information and if  you or someone you know is interested in this type of Chinese Learning,  please let them know and encourage them to enroll during  pre-registration which is 6/4/2011 &amp; 6/11/2011.','MCS Newsletter - 5/14/2011',0,'','publish','closed','open','','mcs-newsletter-5142011','','','2011-05-11 22:41:13','2011-05-12 02:41:13','',0,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=147',0,'post','',0),(148,1,'2011-05-11 22:40:42','2011-05-12 02:40:42','','MCS Newsletter - 5/14/2011',0,'','inherit','open','open','','147-revision','','','2011-05-11 22:40:42','2011-05-12 02:40:42','',147,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=148',0,'revision','',0);
